{"tid":1962221,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"777：人工按通脹調整唔等於加人工","createTime":"2020-04-07T10:24:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-07T11:44:26.000Z","uid":209024,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"52b42e8050c11c01f60918a99dae5f92e7f8ffc2","tid":1962221,"uid":209024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T10:24:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>以後老細加得少過通脹，我係唔係可以同老闆講你無加過人工比我</strong></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>每月加薪 1 萬至年薪 512 萬元 林鄭：按通脹定期調整，非疫情下「加人工」</strong><br />\n<br />\n政府早前向立法會提交的文件指出，林鄭月娥的年薪為 521萬元，較去年增加 12 萬元。林鄭月娥今早出席行政會議前，被記者問及為何在疫情之下加薪，林鄭澄清指是按年按通脹定期調整薪酬，並非加薪。<br />\n<br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥年薪去年已逾 500 萬元，是全球第二高的領導人，今年年薪再從 509 萬元升至 521萬元。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥今日表示個人對薪酬持開放態度，但留意到目前坊間報導令人誤以為在這嚴峻疫情下竟然有官員「加人工」，因此希望作出有關澄清。她<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">強調這次是按年按通脹定期調整薪酬</span></strong></span>，而且有關調整是由去年7月1日起計算，正如立法會議員也由去年 10 月 1 日起按通脹調整薪金。她指出這次只是將周年撥款納入 2020-2021 年預算案，並非有官員在今次預算案提出加人工要求。<br />\n<br />\n被問及會否參考國外官員帶頭減薪或凍薪，林鄭表示現時首要任務是防疫抗疫，支援香港企業和員工，若需要她本人或問責團隊作出什麼舉措達致此目的，她都非常願意做。她又指，過去為展示與民眾齊心抗疫，部分官員曾主動捐出一個月薪酬予非政府機構，往後亦會審慎考慮與民共度時艱該採取的行動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%AF%8F%E6%9C%88%E5%8A%A0%E8%96%AA-1-%E8%90%AC%E8%87%B3%E5%B9%B4%E8%96%AA-512-%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83-%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD-%E6%8C%89%E9%80%9A%E8%84%B9%E5%AE%9A%E6%9C%9F%E8%AA%BF%E6%95%B4-%E9%9D%9E%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E4%B8%8B-%E5%8A%A0%E4%BA%BA%E5%B7%A5/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25AF%258F%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%258A%25A0%25E8%2596%25AA-1-%25E8%2590%25AC%25E8%2587%25B3%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%2596%25AA-512-%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2585%2583-%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD-%25E6%258C%2589%25E9%2580%259A%25E8%2584%25B9%25E5%25AE%259A%25E6%259C%259F%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%2595%25B4-%25E9%259D%259E%25E7%2596%25AB%25E6%2583%2585%25E4%25B8%258B-%25E5%258A%25A0%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25B7%25A5%2F&d=BHyrWEjohbhGCquuSPOYYgoLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=6d0b9bb4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25AF%258F%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%258A%25A0%25E8%2596%25AA-1-%25E8%2590%25AC%25E8%2587%25B3%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%2596%25AA-512-%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2585%2583-%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD-%25E6%258C%2589%25E9%2580%259A%25E8%2584%25B9%25E5%25AE%259A%25E6%259C%259F%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%2595%25B4-%25E9%259D%259E%25E7%2596%25AB%25E6%2583%2585%25E4%25B8%258B-%25E5%258A%25A0%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25B7%25A5%2F&h=daebae3d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%AF%8F%E6%9C%88%E5%8A%A0%E8%96%AA-1-%E8%90%AC%E8%87%B3%E5%B9%B4%E8%96%AA-512-%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83-%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD-%E6%8C%89%E9%80%9A%E8%84%B9%E5%AE%9A%E6%9C%9F%E8%AA%BF%E6%95%B4-%E9%9D%9E%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E4%B8%8B-%E5%8A%A0%E4%BA%BA%E5%B7%A5/</a>"},{"pid":"a6cc3aff3064c3a8a67a6a0ea2d4ff90eca2702c","tid":1962221,"uid":160176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T10:25:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1077c15acdc648ab8153c67c18a418c70bc8120","tid":1962221,"uid":72608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T10:26:02.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥年薪去年已逾 500 萬元，是全球第二高的領導人<br />\n<br />\n唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e35aee0a70f8a626e335e2f25773c9b4724c1cf0","tid":1962221,"uid":48357,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d1077c15acdc648ab8153c67c18a418c70bc8120","tid":1962221,"uid":72608,"like":0,"dislike"